snippet.title: Into The Unknown - Official Trailer #2
snippet.description:
This is the trailer for the Steam release of "Into The Unknown" by indie game developer FYRE Games.  Download it today!

itchio: https://fyre-games.itch.io/into-the-unknown
Gamejolt: http://gamejolt.com/games/into-the-unknown/176057
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/553130?beta=1

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/FyreGamesReal

Thank you to Secret Agent PI for recording this gameplay footage!
Secrect Agent PI: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqlIaf__MV6QrtI_G-lOR6w
